{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67e84a146b","title":"争取于十天内外夺取济南","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ab993b006","index":0,"year":1948,"month":7,"day":16,"articleId":"67e84a146b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"db774f20b6","type":"paragraph","text":"争取于十天内外夺取济南","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"67e84a146b"},{"id":"4dd2151a9c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年7月16日）许、谭，并菜、陈、张，售华东局，中原局：副夜电悉。攻克充州又开八十四师甚好甚慰。望鼓励士气，于尽可能短促时间完成对济南之包围（首先夺取飞机场），并乘胜夺取济南。如果可能，你们应争取于十天内外夺取济南","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"67e84a146b"},{"id":"9d99c4492c","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"67e84a146b"},{"id":"e4b1a5547d","type":"paragraph","text":"铣午[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华东野战军山东兵团司令员许[2]、陈、张，指菜裕、陈士架、张震，当时分别任华东野战军代司令员兼代政治委员、参谋长和副参谋长。[3]华东野战军山东兵团于1948年7月1日包围竞州，12日黄发起总攻，13日下午政占该城，全开守敌2.7万余人，生仔国民党军整编第十二军编第八十四师一部1万余人","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"67e84a146b"}],"page":{"id":"3536ff47db","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"67e84a146b","start":357,"end":357}}}},"__N_SSG":true}